Class CardEvaluatorTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • junit.framework.Assert
      • junit.framework.TestCase
        • com.fsc.pokerserver.test.CardEvaluatorTest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    junit.framework.Test

    public class CardEvaluatorTest
extends junit.framework.TestCase
    JUnit tests for the Seven Card Poker Hand Evaluation. The Evaluation algorithm (TwoPlusTwoHandEvaluator) needs to always determine the winner between two (or more) hands. It should also correctly determine the type of the hand (pair, flush, etc.)
